Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:05.52,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:10.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,休想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:12.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我一定会…
