Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:18.53,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:21.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:22.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,杜宾教官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:25.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:27.35,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,带着大家一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.02,0:00:29.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,逃离这个地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:32.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是…要我们把你抛下吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你一个人不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这样下去你的戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哪怕我会…粉身碎骨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:43.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也要…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:49.57,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:52.50,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:54.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你就是…
Comment: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.19,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,正文
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,向塔露拉 同时射击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,掩护阿米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.07,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她们怎么停止行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:58.84,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是战术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,现在可不是磨磨蹭蹭的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:02.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,全员 按照指示进行撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.01,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:08.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,倒塌的 建筑物废墟中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:12.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有一处空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,从那儿穿过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,只要离开广场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在出口的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:19.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就有个能藏身…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们应该…怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.01,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.90,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}停下！别往雾里面跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,只能死在这里了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:52.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想死…我不想死…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:51.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.44,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}请不要…从我身边离开！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:03:59.90,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这范围…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.74,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,已经就是极限了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,塔露拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.50,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我的手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:20.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,居然对同伴见死…不救…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:23.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:23.92,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,高峰已经过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在第二波到来之前快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,临光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:29.85,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你来带路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:30.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,了解！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.06,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她们抓到了阿米娅的破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:37.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:38.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,快跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:40.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:45.61,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:47.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:48.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,担架已经坏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,让我去把塔露拉给…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:50.87,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我来想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.49,0:04:53.70,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你快带上博士先走！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.04,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,杜宾队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:57.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这里就交给我们！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,别太担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一会儿会合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:01.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,去阻挡塔露拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:08.47,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这里也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:09.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,快撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:09.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:10.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.18,0:05:11.85,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,能听到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:14.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:15.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:17.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我这就来给你开道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:18.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:19.85,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你们先撤！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.15,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.57,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们还能撑得住！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:23.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.03,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,要思考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.61,0:05:28.57,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,现在最应该优先做的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:29.36,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,杜宾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:37.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,了解…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:39.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,重整队形！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你会和阿米娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:51.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一起共同面对这个残酷无情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,保护好阿米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,拜托你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:58.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:05:59.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:01.02,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:08.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,天灾好像已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:12.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,幸好出口没有什么损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.57,0:06:15.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在这里等运输机过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,继续警戒周围的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:20.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,临光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,身为耀骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.88,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,无论是在什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.76,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都要成为指引人们的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:30.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:32.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,别让他们的努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,全都白费！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.48,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:42.69,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace他们的情况…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:46.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都还好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:53.70,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.91,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:04.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没关系的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace他们一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.92,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,会没事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.04,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,罗德岛的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:13.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都是很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:21.64,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,为什么都已经这样了还要战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,真是无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,即使尸骨无存 也还这样奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:31.99,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,了不起的战士！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我会记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:35.95,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,罗德岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我就知道想要顺利的离开没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,搞好关系的第一步是自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:49.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你们可以称呼我为W
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,W…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:55.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是在哪里见过？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.22,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:01.68,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,W！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:03.06,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你有什么目的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:04.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,什么目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.52,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,能不能把博士交给我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:10.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.11,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,认识博士吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.53,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我可是专门为了见她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.95,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,才到这种地方来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.74,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,别和她浪费时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你是叫阿米娅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我的事已经搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,后会有期！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,小兔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:31.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.47,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,再见！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:35.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她们就这么撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:40.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.64,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但我总觉得 她们这帮人别有企图
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:52.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:55.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:56.95,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,队长…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:08:59.91,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,其他的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就只剩下你和我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:05.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:06.87,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.75,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,刚才除了惨叫什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,什么都！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:14.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,别再说下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不然你的伤口会裂开的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:25.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我做了应急处理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,再撑一会儿你就能走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.23,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:29.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你的左手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:33.57,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,至少还有一只能用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:34.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:35.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:36.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你快逃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,队长一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:38.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:39.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,还不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,运输机应该快赶到出口的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,被他们发现就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我去争取点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.04,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你的命可是我废了一只手才换回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这样我的手 也能创造些价值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.47,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:04.22,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.22,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,后会有期…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.36,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.19,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不争气！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:40.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有种…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,非常悲伤的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:50.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Medic…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:54.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}请你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:56.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}节哀顺变…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.57,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有个人这么对我说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.53,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,说在回到家前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,要先把战斗后的眼泪…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好好藏起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.04,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:11.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,回到罗德岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.70,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,看到那块群生地带了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.99,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那些也是源石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就像你在广场看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,源石就像陨石一样 疯狂地砸向地面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这就是天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:56.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在不同地域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,天灾会以雪灾或洪水等形式出现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但它来临的时候 一定会留下源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那么大规模
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,会在地面上成长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,会成长？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,虽然还不清楚具体情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.48,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但是源石结晶的矿脉最终会破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:20.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,释放出一种 叫作源石粒子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,它们似乎会在空中汇聚成云
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:25.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,并且会引发新的天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.07,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,矿石病一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.33,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这和我们感染者的结局也非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:35.75,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,矿石病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,还有人们的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都在持续不断地扩散着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:40.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,杜宾！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你现在很累了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:44.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,最好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.22,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:48.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:51.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但你们不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,现在还是说说话 更轻松一些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:55.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.01,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:12:59.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉让你在这陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.44,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也受益匪浅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,还能看到切尔诺伯格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:09.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那个是在巨大的移动装置上 所建造的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,整座城市都是可以移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:19.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,躲避天灾吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:21.75,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:25.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,世界上绝大部分的城市都是可以移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,天灾发生的地点 可以被预测到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以 通过提前移动城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.01,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就能预防天灾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:34.68,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,为什么切尔诺伯格…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.35,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.73,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这一次的暴动…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,可能有内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:48.74,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是去罗德岛的人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:52.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,目的地是龙门吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,龙门…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是要逃往更前方的城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:02.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,他们应该是从切尔诺伯格逃离的感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这里是机长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.84,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,飞机马上就要降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:54.76,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:55.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我已经听说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,任务…非常辛苦吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:02.44,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.15,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,临光！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你没事太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:06.52,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.48,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有谁能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.40,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,帮我把担架准备一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:11.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我马上拿过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.36,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:17.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你还好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.54,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她现在睡得很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,回到罗德岛后…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.54,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,整个人都放松下来了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她的经历早就超过极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:47.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,您睡醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:48.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:50.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.03,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这一间是会客室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:56.03,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士阁下的房间 现在还正在准备中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以就先让您在这里休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:15:59.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:00.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在罗德岛的舰船中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:05.54,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,您还可以选择继续休息一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:08.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:09.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就由我来带您去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅女士那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:14.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你很聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:15.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.84,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不及博士您的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,换洗的衣服 放置在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅女士目前正在甲板上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,您从这边走过去还有一定的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:28.69,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,机会难得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在过去的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.40,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我会顺便向您介绍一下舰内的设备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.74,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,罗德岛舰船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.91,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,当前正在朝着下一个目的地航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,请问您现在还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.84,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,对于我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:01.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,和今后…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:07.06,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,带路就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:08.64,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,罗德岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是一艘同时搭载了多种多样的医疗设施的综合陆行舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,除了手术所需的仪器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,以及药剂处方之外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.87,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,还备有专门用来研究矿石病的特殊设备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,运转所需的能量全部由舰内提供
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.54,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这台机器会开采并提炼所需要的源石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:32.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们还会加工源石和其它贵金属
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.88,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,并与其他的城市和企业进行贸易上的往来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,居住区域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是为了让干员和住院患者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.06,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,能够舒适的生活而设计的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,由于执行任务和治疗时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.85,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所产生的精神上以及肉体上的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.61,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都能在这里得到缓解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:53.99,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在罗德岛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不论种族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:55.70,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,出身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是感染者还是非感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所有人都能够愉快融洽地在一起生活着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:02.67,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.92,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,由于罗德岛的活动范围很广泛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,因此 也会为大家提供运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,各种武器和装备等作为辅助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:14.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阁下您已到达目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.68,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那么介绍就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:19.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.19,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她身上背负的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:25.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:27.11,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,很沉重…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:34.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,您不去睡真的没关系吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,现在很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一直睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以就跑来外面透透气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,塔露拉说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在脑海中挥之不去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.15,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也许是个只会说空话的理想论者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:04.73,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,可我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.23,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,还是想选择正途
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:07.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,并为此付诸行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.03,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:13.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我所选择的道路是否真的是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也曾深深的怀疑过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,而我的这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好像被她看穿了似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:22.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:25.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这个时候对您说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.75,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,会让您有负担的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace在通信中这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:34.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我会和你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:38.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:41.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,共同面对这个残酷无情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这句话的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,真正的含义 我还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,如果坚持理想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,必然会和现实起冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:55.53,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,他仍然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,相信你会在正确的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:01.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,说的我都赞同…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我不可以再这样迷茫下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.67,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,虽然现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:12.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,没有记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但我会一点点找回的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我一定会协助你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:21.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,实现理想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:23.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:24.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:25.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.23,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,请不要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:29.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们在三天后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,还有新的任务需要去执行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:34.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,请博士好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,把自己恢复得精力充沛才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:39.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在切尔诺伯格的作战中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:53.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们完成了 救出博士您的这一项任务
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,虽然受了很大的损失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:59.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但是获得了不少关于整合运动的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在战略上 可以说是成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:04.73,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,根据分析的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我们可以判断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.36,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,整合运动的下一个攻击目标
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就是炎国的龙门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:12.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,龙门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:15.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,虽然不像切尔诺伯格那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:18.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但龙门对待感染者也是非常苛刻的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:22.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,关于这一点 凯尔希医生已经前往当地了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,与龙门代表的签约工作也在进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,罗德岛就能在市内公开活动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但契约内容还没定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:34.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,因此 希望博士和阿米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.47,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,可以前往龙门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一起帮助凯尔希医生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,签订和龙门之间的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:40.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,签约以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,调查整合运动在龙门的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就是你们的任务了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:45.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.93,0:21:48.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,临光和我 会去负责另外的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.94,0:21:49.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:52.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,整合运动的行动往往出人意料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.69,0:21:54.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一定要多加小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:55.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:58.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:01.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,这一次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:02.91,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,也请多多关照！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:06.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,请多关照！
